===Noun===

'''fauna''' (plural: '''[[faunae]]''' or '''[[faunas]]''')

#[[animal]]s considered as a [[group]]; especially those of a particular [[country]], [[region]], [[time]], etc.
#a [[book]], [[cataloguing]] the animals of a country etc.

